    "function_v0": {
      "doc": "Withdraw from a lending pool, atomically deduct Nestor's fee,\\nand send the net amount to the user.\\n\\n# Arguments\\n* `user`      \\xe2\\x80\\x94 the user's address (must authorize)\\n* `pool`      \\xe2\\x80\\x94 the lending pool contract address (e.g. Blend)\\n* `asset`     \\xe2\\x80\\x94 the SAC token contract address (e.g. USDC)\\n* `amount`    \\xe2\\x80\\x94 total amount to withdraw from the pool (stroops, 7 dec)\\n* `principal` \\xe2\\x80\\x94 original deposit amount (stroops, 7 dec)\\nfee is only charged on (amount \\xe2\\x88\\x92 principal), i.e. yield\\n\\n# Returns\\nTuple of (user_receives, fee_collected) both in stroops.",
